ors quickly mounted their steeds and raced homeward to Themiscrya.::: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Dawnithinia Rivent Darkshade</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(9/7/00 4:21 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Home</span><hr size=1> Dawn scrambled to her saddle as she saw Hipp arrive, green eyes looked at Hipp. Dawn did not know if Hipp knew of the news or not. Her hand reached out to salute her Queen as she spoke quickly.<br>
 &quot;Hipp the Romans are moving close for attack. We've got to get home. I'm sorry this had to come like it is, but if we don't get to Themiscyra we'll loose.&quot;<br>
With that Dawn yanked the reigns of her horse, as it turned to face home. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com/queenhippolyte/BC.html BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Vasilissa</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(9/9/00 4:52 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Quickly Home</span><hr size=1> ::Hipp looks to Dawn and nods, barely slowing her mare to speak to her:: yes, I know.. I had a vision from Hera.  ::then with that she urges her mare into a run and the three take off east towards the City of Amazon.  Hippolyte knows they have no time to waste and rides like a banshee.  The wind blowing her auburn hair.  Her brown eyes wild with the idea of soon to fight.. and the fear of her homeland.::: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/usethramaia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sethra Maia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(9/10/00 7:17 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Quickly Home</span><hr size=1> :: Eventually they reach the outskirts of Themiscrya.Glad to be home. &quot;I'll attend to the Horses while Dawn and the others inform you of what's been happening here since our journey. I will catch up to you after and you can include me on the details.&quot; With that, they arrive into the village.Sethra takes the very worn and tired horses into the stables, she did the cool down and watered and fed them. Skye was running about the stables annoying the other horses. He was glad to be on the ground instead of riding on Sethra's lap.After she finished,she went and met up with Hipp.She was still worried about the talk or war and the effect it will have on the amazons:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessageRange?topicID=7.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessageRange?topicID=7.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessageRange?topicID=7.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a> <b>4</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showPrevMessage?topicID=7.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showNextMessage?topicID=7.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.emailToFriend?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.threadControl?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=2